      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Barroth to a Great Start",
        "Client": "Striking Farmer",
        "Description": "Ta-daaah! I invented this\r\nrevolutionary fertilizer by\r\nmixing all sorts of stuff with\r\na Barroth tail! I\u0027ll make a\r\nkillin\u0027 if I can mass-produce\r\nthis, but I ran outta tail! Can\r\nya go hunt a Barroth for me?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barroth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Queue Barroth et baleine",
        "Client": "Fermier \u00E9clatant",
        "Description": "Tada ! J\u0027ai invent\u00E9 un engrais\r\nr\u00E9volutionnaire en m\u00E9langeant\r\nplein de trucs avec une queue\r\nde Barroth ! \u00C7a va faire un \r\nmalheur, mais j\u0027ai plus de queue !\r\nQuelqu\u0027un pourrait me\r\nchasser un Barroth ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Barroth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il Barroth della fortuna",
        "Client": "Contadina straordinaria",
        "Description": "Tad\u00E0! Ho creato un fertilizzante\r\nrivoluzionario mescolando varie\r\nsostanze con la coda di Barroth.\r\nSe potessi produrlo in serie\r\nsbarcherei il lunario, ma sono\r\nrimasta senza code. Qualcuno\r\ncacci un Barroth per me!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Barroth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Barroth zu einem guten Start",
        "Client": "Streikender Bauer",
        "Description": "Ta-daaa! Ich habe diesen re-\r\nvolution\u00E4ren D\u00FCnger erfunden,\r\nindem ich alles M\u00F6gliche mit\r\nBarroth-Schwanz mischte! Ich\r\nmach gro\u00DFen Reibach bei der\r\nMassenproduktion! Aber ich\r\nbrauche mehr Barroth!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Barroth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Esta cola traer\u00E1 cola!",
        "Client": "Granjera ins\u00F3lita",
        "Description": "\u00A1Tach\u00E1n! He mezclado una cola\r\nde Barroth con todo tipo de\r\ncosas, y me ha salido un\r\nfertilizante revolucionario.\r\nSi lo produzco en masa, me voy\r\na forrar. Pero no me queda\r\ncola. \u00A1C\u00E1zame un Barroth!",
        "Target": "Caza un Barroth",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0440\u0438\u0431\u044B\u043B\u044C\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442 \u0411\u0430\u0440\u0440\u043E\u0442\u0430",
